sentences.sContent: As a result, like the physicians in my study, we make dozens of small, subtle and almost invisible choices about how to spend our time.
sentences.sCn: 所以这结果就变得和我研究组里的医生们一样：做了许许多多琐碎的微不足道的选择和权衡，来安排我们的时间。

sentences.sContent: But there are already people, even dozens of them, who over the years have maintained all these points and live by the truth.
sentences.sCn: 已经有这样的人，数量甚至已经达到了几十个，他们已经坚持上面的标准许多年，只说真话而活着。
